FlashLiteBox
------------

A tiny full-screen flash-based "lightbox" by someone who doesn't know
flash...

Introduction/Code Walkthough at:

  http://overstimulate.com/articles/fullscreen-flash-lightbox



Requirements
============

  swfmill - http://swfmill.org/
  mtasc   - http://mtasc.org/
  make    - gnu know where to find this

How I roll:

  git clone git://github.com/anotherjesse/flashlitebox.git
  cd flashlitebox
  apt-get install mtasc swfmill
  make



HACK WARNING
============

  Ya, it is a crude prototype.  Please fork me and improve it.
  Then you can add your name to the copyright below ;)



